                </a>
                <div id="entryCategoriesWrapper"><ul id="entryCategories"><li><a href="http://www.wired.com/threatlevel/category/hacks-and-cracks/">Hacks and Cracks</a></li><li><a href="http://www.wired.com/threatlevel/category/cybersecurity/">Cybersecurity</a></li></ul></div>            </div>
